{"view":"article","slug":"pyraminx-pyraminx-l4e-v-first","category":"Pyraminx","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Pyraminx","title":{"en":"Pyraminx L4E Method (V-First)"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-l4e-v-first/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-l4e-v-first/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Pyraminx L4E Method (V-First)</strong></p><p><a id=\"_Hlk48940792\"></a>Avg=3.57+0.67+6.29+0.67=11.20.</p><p><strong>V</strong></p><p>Intuitively solve 3 centers, along with 2 of the 3 edges between them. Put unsolved edge on FD. Avg = 3.57.</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-l4e-v-first/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>L4E</strong></p><p><a id=\"_Hlk34388299\"></a>S = R' L R L', H = L R' L' R. When recognize block or bar, do not count yellow edge. Learn intuitively. AUF: red face will be on F after executing. <a id=\"_Hlk48940896\"></a>Default probability=1/32. Avg = 220/35 = 6.29. HR = L R' L' R R = L R' L' R2.</p><p>名称,序号,步数,(1/96概率) 打乱.推U*不再标记记号.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"8\"><p><strong>纯翻Pure Flip [3,3]</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p>二棱翻,01,8</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>二棱翻,02,7</p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p>四棱翻,03,12,1/96</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-l4e-v-first/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-l4e-v-first/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-pyraminx-l4e-v-first/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>H U' R U R'</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"S R U' R'\">S R U' R'</span></p></td><td colspa